Zuccotti Park used to be built for the well-known public, however the weeks-long protest has raised issues amongst vicinity enterprise proprietors and residents about sanitation.
The protest campaign commenced in July with the launch of a marketing campaign website calling for a march and a sit-in at the New York Stock Exchange.
